text: What if Humans painted Earth Blue?
Oh No.
I just painted my house Red.
Oh AumSum.
Firstly, if Humans painted Earth Blue.
Some people may think there is water all around, they may take out their boats.
Secondly, if Humans painted Earth Blue.
People who are not fond of blue color will definitely leave for a different planet.
Thirdly, if Humans painted Earth Blue.
Sky, Water and earth will all appear blue.
Even aliens might get curious and start visiting our planet.
Fourthly, if Humans painted Earth Blue.
Blue whales will be extremely happy.
Other colored fishes might leave for a different planet.
Fifthly, if Humans painted Earth Blue.
Traffic signals will not show green again.
There will be long traffic lines everywhere.
Lastly, if Humans painted Earth Blue.
People who just colored their hair may get shell-shocked.
